          <versionCode>00</versionCode>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Campaign Sunlight Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Federal Election Commission to create a website that&nbsp;allows the public to view political advertisements. The sponsor of a political advertisement shall provide the advertisement to the commission within a certain time frame from when it was first disseminated and, if the advertisement refers to any source such as an article or quotation, shall also provide the full contents of that source. </p>]]></text>
